.sp
Besides, by using zstyle command, you can change default value:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zstyle ":zplug:tag" use "*\&.sh"
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.SH "EXAMPLES"
.sp
Case of :
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zplug "b4b4r07/enhancd" \e
    as:plugin, \e
    use:"*\&.sh"
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
.sp
Case of GitHub Release:
.sp
.if n \{\
.RS 4
.\}
.nf
$ zplug "peco/peco" \e
    as:command, \e
    from:gh\-r, \e
    use:"*darwin*"
.fi
.if n \{\
.RE
.\}
